What you need to know:

I narrow it down for him, to choose between Korea and Harambee Stars who are ranked 102nd in the world. “Aaah…Ugali and kuku…or ugali and samaki anytime. In Korea, I don’t know what they eat there. I love Kenya so let’s see what happens,” he beams as his right hand taps the left side of his chest as an expression of love.